levels.helpHTML:
The version pairs are s6/s6j and peyg/peygj; the medalless level is bp.

The level groupings are mostly obvious; the movement group is intended to be hover-based/fluddless movement levels, and was defined in Nov 2020 as:

b3 b3s b4 b6 b6s r1 r2 r3 r4 r4s r5
g1s p2 p2s p3 p6s s2 s2s s3 s4 s4s
n1 n2 n6 n6s q3 q4 q6 c

players.anonHTML: Hidden names: Some player names are hidden by default (to an initial followed by a period, like A.) for abuse-related reasons. This leaderboard provides full data about all known speedrun records, and so has the option to show these names, but it is considered important for readers to be informed of why these names were hidden before using this option.
